---
// About.astro - Sección sobre mí
---

<section id="about" class="section bg-background-secondary dark:bg-background-dark-secondary">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">About me</h2>
      <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-primary mx-auto"></div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute -top-4 -left-4 w-24 h-24 bg-primary/20 rounded-lg -z-10"></div>
          <div class="absolute -bottom-4 -right-4 w-24 h-24 bg-primary/20 rounded-lg -z-10"></div>
          <img 
            src="/images/Desktop_Image.png" 
            alt="Foto de perfil" 
            class="w-full max-w-md mx-auto rounded-lg shadow-lg"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 hidden md:flex">
          <div class="border rounded-lg p-4 shadow-lg">
            <h5 class="font-bold mb-2">Personal Information</h5>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="font-medium mr-2">Location:</span> 
                <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">La Habana, Cuba</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="font-medium mr-2">Languages:</span> 
                <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Spanish (Native), English (B1 - Intermediate)</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start">
                <span class="font-medium mr-2">Available:</span> 
                <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Freelance Projects, Part-time / Full-time</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary">David Daniel Salazar Jiménez</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          I'm a developer passionate about creating digital solutions that combine cutting-edge technology with intuitive design. <br>
          With +3 years of experience in front-end web development, I specialize in building scalable, responsive, and high-performance web applications.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          My focus is on code quality, user experience, effective problem-solving, and even more so, on progressing every day to become a better programmer and a better person.
        </p>
        <!-- Aquí puedes añadir más texto si lo deseas -->
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 mt-8 md:hidden">
      <div class="border rounded-lg p-4 shadow-lg">
        <h5 class="font-bold mb-2">Personal Information</h5>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="font-medium mr-2">Location:</span> 
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">La Habana, Cuba</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="font-medium mr-2">Languages:</span> 
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Spanish (Native), English (B1 - Intermediate)</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start">
            <span class="font-medium mr-2">Available:</span> 
            <span class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">Freelance Projects, Part-time / Full-time</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section> 